2017 The 11th International Service Innovation Conference




The College of Service Industries, Minghsin University of Science and Technology (CSIMUST), organizes its 11th International Service Innovation Conference, April 26, 2017, Hsinchu County, Taiwan. The aim of the conference is to bring together scholars, specialists, and students from all areas of tourism, hospitality, MICE development, leisure management, child education, senior citizen service, and other related fields. Theoretical and empirical research knowledge will be shared and discussed by keynote speeches, paper presentations, panel of industry-education coordinated development, and boards of innovative products of service. Research articles and reviews in the following fields are very welcome:

Read more about 2017 The 11th International Service Innovation Conference 






